{
  "stem": "25591.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in his 30s.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- but I don't want to-- to give the impression for a moment that I was a collaborator of his or a friend of his.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was a-- a totally unimportant young person who looked up to him and who admired him, and who was thrilled to be able to-- to-- to assist in the most menial ways.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw him at the railroad station on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and it's very difficult for me now to separate the pictures I-- I have seen since and what I remember from 1944.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it's more than a half a century ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I can only say that he dominated my thinking and my actions during those months of-- the latter half of 1944, the first few weeks of '45.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians liberated Pest first, Buda about a months later in mid-January.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was arrested-- which I didn't know at the time-- on January 17.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I really was conscious of his-- his work for about a half a year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not at the level where, you know, I would-- I would know any of these things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I believe I knew who Eichmann was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- I knew-- I believe I knew the name Eichmann, but I wouldn't swear to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's so difficult, you know, after all these decades and after all the reading I have done, to sort of try to project back to the year 1944 and-- and remember what my frame of mind was or what my scope of knowledge was.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very limited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very limited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- like everybody else around me, I was living from day to day.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
